title: Saints Row IV Soundtrack (all stations) (MP3 @320)
description:
The complete Saints Row IV radio station soundtrack ripped directly from the game.
Each station is separated into their own folder.

Mp3 CBR 320kbps, 2ch, 44.1khz, 16 bit

All tags and album artwork (radio station logos)

Some tracks sound like they are mono, this is straight from the game... blame the source!

Small gain increase of 3-5 dB to compensate for low volume from the game... again blame the source!  Overall not loud, not quiet.
